<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0746c04shiGuiYu"><lb
ed="T" n="0746c04"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0746c04"/><head><date from-iso="+0907-06-10" key="j20524952058534" to-iso="+0923-12-22">梁</date><supplied resp="sgsz">今</supplied><placeName key="PL000000023307"><placeName>東京</placeName><placeName>相國寺</placeName></placeName><ptr target="#n273"/><persName key="A009874">歸嶼</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0746c05"/><persName key="A009874">釋歸嶼</persName>，姓<name>湄</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000016347">壽春</placeName>人也。父<persName key="A009875">元旭</persName>知<ref type="person" target="#A009874">子</ref>敏<lb
ed="T" n="0746c06"/>利，授以《詩》、《書》，誦覽記憶，彌見過群。從諸子<lb
ed="T" n="0746c07"/>而竊願出塵，<ref type="person" target="#A009875">父</ref>母允其頻請，乃<anchor xml:id="beg0746sgsz10"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0746sgsz10"/>本郡<placeName key="PL000000016332">開<lb
ed="T" n="0746c08"/>元寺</placeName><persName key="A009877">道宗<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>為力生<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1063"/>焉。未及周星<ptr type="glossary" target="#g122"/>，念通<lb
ed="T" n="0746c09"/>《法華》、《仁王》<ptr target="#n198"/>二經。登于<date key="j20424742042839" from-iso="+0880-01-01" to-iso="+0880-12-31">弱冠</date>，而全戒足，矜持<lb
ed="T" n="0746c10"/>三行<ptr target="#n1064"/>，靡曠四儀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1065"/>，習聽新章<ptr target="#n902"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0746005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>寺</sic><corr>尋</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0746005"/>通講授。後<lb
ed="T" n="0746c11"/>聞<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛京</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042002">三輔</placeName>經、論盛行，結侶求師。僅于十<lb
ed="T" n="0746c12"/>載，疏通性、相，精大、小乘，名數一支，「因明」一<lb
ed="T" n="0746c13"/>學，《俱舍》<ptr target="#n1429"/>、《唯識》<ptr target="#n767"/>、《維摩》、《上生》<ptr target="#n772"/>，皆深藏若虛也。復<lb
ed="T" n="0746c14"/>往<ref type="place" target="#PL000000024155">南<name>燕</name></ref>就<persName key="A009862">暉<roleName>公</roleName></persName>，重覆所學，研朱益丹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1067"/>，猶<lb
ed="T" n="0746c15"/>慨義章未為盡善。乃之今<placeName key="PL000000023307"><placeName>東京</placeName><placeName>相國寺</placeName></placeName>，遂<lb
ed="T" n="0746c16"/>糅《新鈔》，講訓克勤<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g560"/>，門生領悟。時<persName key="A006574">朱梁<roleName>後主</roleName></persName>與<lb
ed="T" n="0746c17"/><persName key="A009874">嶼</persName>丱角<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g635"/>同學庠序，狎密情濃，隔面年深。<ref type="date" target="#j20545912054924">即<lb
ed="T" n="0746c18"/>位半載</ref>，下詔訪<ref type="person" target="#A009874">之</ref>。<persName key="A009874">嶼</persName>雖知故舊，終歲不<lb
ed="T" n="0746c19"/>言。事不可逃，應召方入。<ref type="person" target="#A006574">帝</ref>見悲喜交集，宣<lb
ed="T" n="0746c20"/>賚豐厚。時屬<date key="j20548182054818" when-iso="+0913-10-19">嘉慶節</date><ptr target="#n1066"/>，曾下勅止絕天下薦<lb
ed="T" n="0746c21"/>僧道恩命，其年獨賜<persName key="A009874">嶼</persName>紫衣，仍號<persName key="A009874">演法大<lb
ed="T" n="0746c22"/>師</persName>。兩街威儀<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g261"/>迎導，至<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023307">寺</ref>，兼勅<placeName key="PL000000023309"><placeName>東塔</placeName><placeName>御容院</placeName></placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0746c23"/>為<placeName key="PL000000023309">長講院</placeName>。時<ref type="person" target="#A003732"><name>閩</name>帥</ref>，以<date key="j20548182054818" when-iso="+0913-10-19">聖節</date>進《金剛經》一藏，<lb
ed="T" n="0746c24"/>絹三百匹，盡賜<persName key="A009874">嶼</persName>焉，法侶榮之。然覩舊鈔<lb
ed="T" n="0746c25"/>有所不安，未極其理，遂搜抉精義於三<lb
ed="T" n="0746c26"/>載，著成二十卷，號曰《會要草字》，寫畢進呈。<lb
ed="T" n="0746c27"/><ref type="person" target="#A006574">帝</ref>覽賞歎，勅令入藏，<persName key="A009874">嶼</persName>苦辭乃止。如是十<lb
ed="T" n="0746c28"/>五年中，唱導無怠，學徒<persName key="A000786">繼榮</persName>、<persName key="A000785">贍公</persName>相繼傳<lb
ed="T" n="0746c29"/>持。至<placeName key="PL000000057656">後唐</placeName><date key="j20632322063232" when-iso="+0936-11-01"><name>清泰</name>三年十月十日</date>，謂門人<persName key="A009883"><anchor xml:id="beg0746sgsz12"/>洪<anchor xml:id="end0746sgsz12"/><pb ed="T" n="0747a" xml:id="T50.2061.0747a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0747a01"/>演</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009874">余</ref>氣力惙然，無常將至，<ref type="person" target="#A009883">汝</ref>好住修進。」<lb
ed="T" n="0747a02"/>焚香合掌，初夜長逝，春秋七十五，僧臘五十<lb
ed="T" n="0747a03"/>五。即以<date key="j20632402063240" when-iso="+0936-11-09">其月十八日</date>遷塔於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023327">京</ref>東郊寺莊東<lb
ed="T" n="0747a04"/>岡焉。</p>
